## v2.7.0 (2024-04-11)

[GitHub release]

The code released in v2.7.0 is practically identical to that of v2.7.0b1.

### What's Changed

#### Packaging

* Reorganize `pyproject.toml` sections by [@Viicos] in [#8899]
* Bump `pydantic-core` to `v2.18.1` by [@sydney-runkle] in [#9211]
* Adopt `jiter` `v0.2.0` by [@samuelcolvin] in
[pydantic/pydantic-core#1250]

#### New Features

* Extract attribute docstrings from `FieldInfo.description` by [@Viicos] in
[#6563]


